title: My 10 Books (PDF) - May 2016 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 books in PDF format. All have OCR & Covers:

01. How Does One Cut a Triangle (2nd Ed) by Alexander Soifer
02. Inside Your Brain (Brain Works) by Eric H. Chudler, Ph.D.
03. Introduction to Computers by Munishwar Gulati
04. Knots in Use (4th Ed) by Colin Jarman
05. Management of Labor and Delivery (2nd Ed) by George A. Macones MD
06. Moonstruck - How Lunar Cycles Affect Life by Ernest Naylor
07. Old Forts of the Great Lakes - Sentinels in the Wilderness by James P. Barry
08. Recreational Problems in Geometric Dissections and How to Solve Them by Harry Lindgren
09. Science Fiction and Fantasy Artists of the Twentieth Century by Jane Frank
10. Teach Yourself  Correct English by B.A.Pythian
